title: Website Profile Not Updating
body:
My profile on the website isn't displaying the correct level or icon. I've heard posting can fix it, so I'm testing here.

edit: The level appears to be correct now, but not the icon.

replies.body:
same problem maybe a comment fixes this
edit:yes it does

Sometimes the Icon can take a while to update. Unfortunately syncing between our Boards and Summoner profiles isn't perfect, but it should update at some point! ^.^

Let me know if you have any other questions.
